# Font files directory
#
# To use custom Inter fonts:
# 1. Download Inter from https://rsms.me/inter/download/
# 2. Extract and place these TTF files here:
#    - Inter-Regular.ttf
#    - Inter-Medium.ttf
#    - Inter-Bold.ttf
#
# The app will fall back to system sans-serif fonts if these are not present.
